General.Name: Kingwaytek Technology Co Ltd
General.Description: Kingwaytek Technology Co., Ltd. produces electronic maps and develops GIS systems in Taiwan. It offers telecommunications maps, 3D maps, and high-definition maps for self-driving cars; and Leke Navigation Wangquan 3D, a mobile navigation software that provides 3D map, traffic lights along the way, road markings, signs, surrounding landmarks, viaducts, and navigation guidelines under the bridge. The company also provides Leke Navigation King TM series that offers professional car networking navigation software for cars and machines; and Leker Interchange, a transfer and pedestrian route guidance service. In addition, it offers big data services that are used in smart traffic diversion and enhancing public transportation services; Leke store; self-driving technology solutions; and bus fleet management services. The company was founded in 1998 and is based in Taipei, Taiwan.
